This year has been one I’ll never forget, overwhelmed just writing this, holding back tears of joy, not sure how I got here but here I am. It’s so good to see all this hard work paying off, seeing the blessings and I’m feelin so thankful and still so inspired…. here’s just a handful of the things that made this year unforgettable, Happy New Year everyone! Wishing everybody the best for 2024! I love and appreciate you all! Quick list mainly for me cause writing this out feels cool haha
- Started off the year at Disney 🌎
- filmed another year of VPR💜 
-Bought a house! We now call home 🏡 
- Played the BIGGEST shows of my life/ sold out shows🤯
- Signed a Vegas Residency! Dream come true✨🔥
- Took Ally to London!❤️
- Studio time 🙌
- And the greatest gift of all! Hippie my best friend my pup my lil guy is back home….. we will love him until the end of time. 🐶 (we also love the cats 🐈 🐈‍⬛ so much) 
Couldn’t have done all this without my team, my family, friends and most of all my love @allylewber ❤️
